text: Jussi Vesterinen (born 9 May 1949) is a Finnish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 52 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Finland Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Viitasaari
